prompts.text:
Inspect the screenshot and judge each requirement below independently.

Requirements:
{numbered_requirements}

For each requirement, decide: is it SATISFIED (true) or VIOLATED (false) in the rendered image? Be strict about overlap, overflow, clipping, scrollbars, even spacing, and alignment — these are exactly the failures you must catch.

Respond with ONLY a JSON object:
{{
  "verdicts": [
    {{"index": 1, "satisfied": true|false, "evidence": "what you see in the image"}},
    ...
  ]
}}
Return exactly one verdict per requirement, in order.
